prediction.sparql:
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?startDate WHERE {
  fb:m.093xn8 fb:tv.tv_character.appeared_in_tv_program ?appearance .
  ?appearance fb:tv.regular_tv_appearance.series fb:m.03m8sg .
  ?appearance fb:tv.regular_tv_appearance.from ?startDate .
}
ORDER BY ?startDate
LIMIT 1

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?position ?positionLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.02yy8 fb:government.politician.government_positions_held ?pos .
  ?pos fb:government.government_position_held.office_position_or_title ?position .
  ?pos fb:government.government_position_held.to ?to .
  FILTER ( ?to < "1933-03-04" ^^ xsd:date ) OPTIONAL {
    ?position rdfs:label ?positionLabel .
    FILTER ( lang( ?positionLabel ) = 'en' )
  }
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?to )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?profession ?professionLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.0dq5yyl fb:people.person.profession ?profession .
  ?profession rdfs:label ?professionLabel .
  FILTER ( lang( ?professionLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?spouseName WHERE {
  fb:m.018fzs fb:people.person.spouse_s ?marriage .
  ?marriage fb:people.marriage.spouse ?spouse .
  ?spouse fb:type.object.name ?spouseName .
  ?spouse fb:people.person.gender fb:m.02zsn .
  FILTER ( ?spouse != fb:m.018fzs )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?wife ?wifeName WHERE {
  fb:m.0cm83 fb:people.person.spouse_s ?marriage .
  ?marriage fb:people.marriage.spouse ?wife .
  ?wife fb:people.person.gender fb:m.02zsn .
  ?wife rdfs:label ?wifeName .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?wifeName ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?championship ?start_date WHERE {
  fb:m.0jm3v fb:sports.sports_team.championships ?championship .
  ?championship fb:time.event.start_date ?start_date .
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?start_date )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?team ?teamLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.02d9k fb:sports.pro_athlete.teams ?roster1 .
  ?roster1 fb:sports.sports_team_roster.team fb:m.01k2yr .
  ?roster1 fb:sports.sports_team_roster.from ?fromLA .
  fb:m.02d9k fb:sports.pro_athlete.teams ?roster2 .
  ?roster2 fb:sports.sports_team_roster.team ?team .
  ?roster2 fb:sports.sports_team_roster.to ?to .
  FILTER ( ?to <= ?fromLA ) .
  ?team rdfs:label ?teamLabel .
  FILTER ( lang( ?teamLabel ) = "en" )
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?to )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?deity ?deityLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.0flw86 fb:religion.religion.deities ?deity .
  ?deity rdfs:label ?deityLabel
  FILTER ( lang( ?deityLabel ) = "en" && regex( ?deityLabel , "^Allah$" , "i" ) )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?institution ?institutionName WHERE {
  fb:m.0271_s fb:people.person.education ?education .
  ?education fb:education.education.institution ?institution .
  ?institution fb:type.object.name ?institutionName .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?institutionName ) = '' || LANGMATCHES( LANG( ?institutionName ) , 'en' ) )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?place ?placeLabel ?county ?countyLabel WHERE {
  ?place rdfs:label ?placeLabel .
  FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?placeLabel ) , "st paul" ) ) ?place fb:location.location.containedby ?county .
  ?county fb:location.location.containedby fb:m.07z1m .
  ?county rdfs:label ?countyLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?placeLabel ) = "en" && LANG( ?countyLabel ) = "en" )
}
LIMIT 10

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?championship ?championshipLabel ?year ?teamLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.070xg rdfs:label ?teamLabel .
  fb:m.070xg fb:sports.sports_team.championships ?championship .
  ?championship fb:type.object.type fb:american_football.super_bowl .
  ?championship rdfs:label ?championshipLabel .
  ?championship fb:time.event.start_date ?startDate .
  BIND( year( xsd:dateTime ( ?startDate ) ) AS ?year )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?country WHERE {
  fb:m.07hcc fb:base.ancientegypt.tomb_owner.tomb_owned ?tomb .
  ?tomb fb:location.location.containedby ?country .
  ?country fb:type.object.name ?name .
  FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?name ) , "egypt" ) )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?language ?languageLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.0chghy fb:location.country.languages_spoken ?language .
  ?language rdfs:label ?languageLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?languageLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?actor ?actorName WHERE {
  fb:m.06yykb fb:film.film.starring ?performance .
  ?performance fb:film.performance.actor ?actor .
  ?performance fb:film.performance.character ?character .
  ?character fb:type.object.name ?characterName .
  ?actor fb:type.object.name ?actorName .
  FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?characterName ) , "roxanne" ) )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?actor ?actorLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.035szd fb:tv.tv_character.appeared_in_tv_program ?appearance .
  ?appearance fb:tv.regular_tv_appearance.actor ?actor .
  ?appearance fb:tv.regular_tv_appearance.series fb:m.019nnl .
  ?appearance fb:tv.regular_tv_appearance.from ?startDate .
  FILTER ( xsd:dateTime ( ?startDate ) < "2000-01-01T00:00:00" ^^ xsd:dateTime || ! BOUND( ?startDate ) ) OPTIONAL {
    ?actor rdfs:label ?actorLabel .
    FILTER ( lang( ?actorLabel ) = "en" )
  }
}
ORDER BY ?startDate
LIMIT 1

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?start_date WHERE {
  fb:m.0jmfb fb:sports.sports_team.championships ?championship .
  ?championship fb:time.event.start_date ?start_date .
}
ORDER BY ?start_date
LIMIT 1

PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?country ?countryName WHERE {
  fb:m.09889g fb:people.person.place_of_birth ?placeOfBirth .
  ?placeOfBirth fb:location.location.containedby ?country .
  ?country rdf:type fb:location.country .
  ?country rdfs:label ?countryName .
  FILTER ( lang( ?countryName ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>

  fb:m.02896 fb:sports.sports_team.colors ?color .
  ?color rdfs:label ?colorLabel .
  FILTER ( lang( ?colorLabel ) = 'en' )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?spouseLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.05np4c fb:people.person.spouse_s ?marriage .
  ?marriage fb:people.marriage.spouse fb:m.09k5l7w .
  fb:m.09k5l7w rdfs:label ?spouseLabel .
  FILTER ( lang( ?spouseLabel ) = "en" )
}
LIMIT 1

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?spouse ?spouseName WHERE {
  fb:m.03p77 fb:people.person.spouse_s ?marriage .
  ?marriage fb:people.marriage.spouse ?spouse .
  ?spouse rdfs:label ?spouseName
  FILTER ( lang( ?spouseName ) = 'en' ) FILTER ( ?spouse = fb:m.01_tz )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?championship ?start_date WHERE {
  fb:m.0713r fb:sports.sports_team.championships ?championship .
  ?championship fb:time.event.start_date ?start_date .
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?start_date )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?sportLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.02d9k fb:sports.pro_athlete.sports_played_professionally ?sportsPlayed .
  ?sportsPlayed fb:sports.pro_sports_played.sport ?sport .
